{"tid":2198668,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【基因研究】到底香港人接近泰族，定南島族多啲？","createTime":"2020-09-11T13:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T02:31:04.000Z","uid":276716,"like":31,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ee52a6680cb32376526412a7ff27d03cb77adf","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHB5zjr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHB5zjr.jpg&h=c95ed977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基因証據顯示，粵人同三個族群有超密切關係。<br />\n<br />\n1. 泰/傣<br />\n2. 阿美族<br />\n3. 泰雅族<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">越王勾踐講泰語？</span><br />\n學者參考泰語去破譯越絕書，証明咗越國係講類似泰語嘅語言。而基因研究亦得出相同結果，東亞東南沿海係泰族原居地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFqh9UG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFqh9UG.jpg&h=c93fc831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">蜑家人源自南島民族</span><br />\n阿美族、泰雅族係南島語族。基因研究証實咗Wilhelm Solheim嘅理論，一支南島語族曾經散佈到華南沿岸。<br />\n睇埋生活形態、文化，水上人應該就係呢支南島語族嘅後代。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">粵係混合民族</span><br />\n粵地喺北方人入侵前應該係咁樣嘅，內陸主要係泰族從事農業，而海邊嘅南島族維持住海洋生活。兩者撈埋一齊，就形成粵人。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">香港自古同粵地分野</span><br />\n香港同粵地嘅最大分別，就係呢度嘅南島成分零舍高，原因在於香港島嶼密集，海岸線曲折，形同太平洋島嶼。呢個差異一直持續到北方人南侵之後。珠三角先後被被漢化粵人墾殖，但直到開埠，香港仍然係水上人嘅聚居地。<br />\n<br />\n睇埋<br />\n<br />\n文化角度証明香港屬於太平洋文化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2173692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2173692</a><br />\n<br />\n粵語係泰語近親<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1969593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1969593</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.biorxiv.org/content/biorxiv/early/2017/07/13/162982.full.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biorxiv.org%2Fcontent%2Fbiorxiv%2Fearly%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F162982.full.pdf&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fv4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=0cb1f55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.biorxiv.org/content/biorxiv/early/2017/07/13/162982.full.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"c6dff607d4c9814cb3c877add4715e2864572449","tid":2198668,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"aa88f159c89b5ff466995b6fc2a3d56bb203d174","tid":2198668,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34a15afb923d26967f010ebeac23de1649f078a","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"基因研究証實，粵人嘅同胞：阿美族<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nD6AWD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnD6AWD0.jpg&h=de655cc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70f582fd27d96f033bbbcbcada2bc5672842fe43","tid":2198668,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"睇血源定睇文化先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fe1fdf2cc56a3c16812256913baa5f8c28e098","tid":2198668,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Bm5zqu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Bm5zqu.png&h=fdb1f459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23andme 話我有泰族血統"},{"pid":"a2fec5cfcfeef8da884b3df630c48d68d86a39b9","tid":2198668,"uid":92442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70f582fd27d96f033bbbcbcada2bc5672842fe43","tid":2198668,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"睇血源定睇文化先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit