ved from Austronesia during the Ice Age. The original inhabitants of Indonesia and the Philippines might have been related to Dravidians of Southern India. Y-haplogroup C, which has been associated with the first migration of modern humans out of Africa towards Asia, is relatively frequent in Kerala (southern tip of India) and Borneo. These early Austronesians are thought to have been the ancestors of the Ice Age settlers of Japan (Y-haplogroups C1a1 and D1b)."},{"pid":"e28d978e81ace7cf885d81e9d5a8dd84844a184d","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"f4a0e8973ed441621023ad1792dae63d5e20edad","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:59:16.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"1be261f6dbbc18abdb2d3287b0c3288eb06113f1","tid":2198668,"uid":205099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d34a15afb923d26967f010ebeac23de1649f078a","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"基因研究証實，粵人嘅同胞：阿美族<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nD6AWD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnD6AWD0.jpg&h=de655cc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:23:30.000Z","msg":"呢個係支那人"},{"pid":"f22ba3f11f93ce44a75e37a095dca92473890351","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"729f50e22546ff854a8ee04a86d529e7fc348dbf","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"9a408f7fc41caadb88b301bc8ba8d5ffb156afd5","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"8024ac547cecb1f72a06cbd02f66da07b77f8d12","tid":2198668,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T